about.summary: A jazzy skin for the Django Admin-Interface

name: django-grappelli
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "3.0.2" %}

package:
  name: django-grappelli
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/d/django-grappelli/django-grappelli-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 604cfce601a5246690e4e2d9b3c6a0db57bccbefdba5e81733f2db9a7ba62fac

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3
    - django

test:
  imports:
    - grappelli
    - grappelli.templatetags
    - grappelli.views
    - grappelli.dashboard
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: http://django-grappelli.readthedocs.org
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A jazzy skin for the Django Admin-Interface

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - kwilcox
    - ocefpaf
